race.comment: STAR REBEL (2) is progressing well claiming his 3rd career win latest, scoring by 6 lengths (22.46) at this track. Ran the fastest time on the program in his latest win. Well placed and will be tough to beat. HARA HACHI BU (7) is in sizzling form lately, rocketing around Ballarat in 22.11 to score two back then following on with a 22.53 win over 400m at this track. Has the ability and can measure up again. PAW GAETON (1) is progressing well with another good run, placing by 10 lengths (23.15) in a Mix 6/7 H at this track. Can measure up. OH BISCUIT (4) placed last time and cannot be ignored.
